title: Documentation - Vertex AI gRPC API
abstract:
# Documentation - Vertex AI gRPC API
This is the gRPC API reference for the Online Predictions pre-trained API that is included with Vertex AI on Google Distributed Cloud Hosted (GDCH). Use this API to get online predictions using your custom-trained models.
For information about this API, see [Send an online prediction request](/distributed-cloud/hosted/docs/latest/gdch/application/ao-user/quickstart-op#send-an-online-prediction-request)
